                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-2" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Our thoughtfully conducted Microsoft Azure Administrator AZ-104 certification training ensures that all our participants get:</p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>A copy of the course material</li>
                                                <li>Access to Microsoft Azure Labs</li>
                                                <li>Course completion certificate</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-3">3. Are there any reference materials for the Microsoft Azure Administrator Training?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-3" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>While there are no direct reference materials for Microsoft Azure Administrator AZ-104 courses, you can visit <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/learn/certifications/exams/az-104" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">the official Microsoft Azure Administrator AZ-104 page</a> to understand:</p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>What is this Microsoft Azure Administrator AZ-104 course is all about</li>
                                                <li>When was the Microsoft Azure Administrator AZ-104 course was last updated</li>
                                                <li>Skills Measured for Microsoft Azure AZ-104 certification exam</li>
                                                <li>Self-paced Microsoft Learn video modules</li>
                                                <li>AZ-104 certification exam resources, and more</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-4">4. How does the Microsoft Azure Administrator Training help me?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-4" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The Microsoft Azure Administrator Az-104 training is a great way to understand one of the most popular cloud environments in the world. From setting up the cloud network for an organization to scaling it up, managing identities and governance, and security, the Azure Administrator training, with a balanced mix of classroom lessons and lab sessions ensures that you get real-world experience of the day-to-day work of a cloud administrator. The training will also prepare you to ace the Microsoft Azure Administrator AZ-104 exam and validate your experience.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-5">5. What qualifications do I need to take up the Azure Administrator Training?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-5" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Anybody with 6 months of experience in the Microsoft Azure environment will find this AZ-104 course beneficial for their career. This Microsoft Azure Administrator certification course is ideal for Azure Administrators, Cloud Administrators, System Administrators, and anybody who is interested in gaining a proper understanding of Microsoft Azure in an enterprise context can take up this training.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-6">6. Is KnowledgeHut an accredited training provider to deliver Microsoft Trainings?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-6" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, KnowledgeHut is a Learning Action Pack Partner authorized to deliver Microsoft Trainings.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-7">7. What are the different learning modalities for taking up the AZ – 104 Training?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-7" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>You can take up this Microsoft Azure Administrator certification training course in multiple delivery modes that include:</p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Instructor-led classroom training</li>
                                                <li>Instructor-led Live online training</li>
                                                <li>Corporate/on-site training</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-8">8. How much does the Microsoft Azure Administrator AZ 104 Certification Exam cost?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-8" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>As of December 2021, the Microsoft Azure Expert and Associate level certification exams are priced at US$165. The exam cost is usually priced according to the currency values in specific regions and countries. Do keep in mind that the exam prices are subject to change and may vary depending on the additional taxes applicable in some countries and regions.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-9">9. Does the Course Fee Include the AZ 104 Examination Fee as well?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-9" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>No, the course fee does not include the Microsoft Azure Administrator AZ-104 examination fee. By taking up the AZ-104 training, you are only paying for the training and not for the exam. The certification exam cost for AZ-104 is USD 165 and the exam must be taken from Pearson Vue.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-10">10. What is the validity of my Microsoft Azure Administrator Associate Certification?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-10" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Upon clearing your AZ-104 examination, your Microsoft Azure Administrator certification will be valid for two years. After the validity period of two years, your certification will not be current anymore, but it will be still showcased under a different section with Exam code and year mentioned along with it.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-11">11. How many questions does the AZ - 104 Certification Exam have?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-11" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Candidates need to answer between 40-60 questions. However, the number of questions may change as and when changes in technology and job roles occur.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-12">12. What is the passing score for the AZ - 104 Certification Exam?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-12" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Candidates will need to score 700 (on a scale of 1-1000) to pass the Microsoft Azure Administrator Associate exam. On each exam domain, a minimum score of 35 percent needs to be scored.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-13">13. If I don’t clear the AZ - 104 Certification Exam in my first attempt, how can I retake the exam?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-13" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Candidates must wait for 24 hours to retake the AZ-104 exam. Candidates can also log in to their certification dashboard to reschedule the exam.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-14">14. What is the passing score for the Microsoft Azure Administrator AZ-104 exam?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-14" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The passing score for the Microsoft Azure Administrator Az-104 exam is 700.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-15">15. Which courses should I take before and after the Azure Administrator course?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-15" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>It is recommended that candidates for the Microsoft Azure Administrator (AZ-104) training take the Microsoft Azure Fundamentals – AZ 900 before.</p>
                                            <p>And the Designing and Implementing Microsoft DevOps Solutions – AZ 400 after this course.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-16">16. What does a Microsoft Partner mean?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-16" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>A Microsoft Partner is a training provider that has been authorized by Microsoft to provide programs to professionals based on Microsoft Certifications. This accreditation represents Microsoft’s acknowledgment of the training provider’s ability to provide training programs in line with Microsoft’s best practices.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="cert-and-exam-section" id="finance-related-queries-2">
                            <h3>Finance-Related Queries</h3>
                            <div class="course-cert-faq-content accordion-cards custom-cards" id="faq-accordion-2">
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-1">1. Can I cancel my enrolment? Do I get a refund?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-1" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>With our 100% Satisfaction Guarantee policy, you are assured of the highest standards of quality. At KnowledgeHut, we strive to ensure that your learning experience with us is beyond reproach. However, if for any reason your expectations are not met, we will refund the course fee in accordance with our <a href="#" target="_blank">100% Satisfaction Guarantee policy.</a></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-2">2. Can I switch the start date to my Microsoft Azure Administrator training?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-2" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, you can switch the start date to your Microsoft Power BI training, with prior notice of at least 24 hrs and subject to availability in the desired batch.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-3">3. Is there a money-back guarantee for the Microsoft Azure Administrator Training?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-3" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, we have a 100% money-back guarantee in line with our <a href="#" target="_blank">100% Satisfaction Guarantee policy.</a></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-4">4. Are scholarships available for the Microsoft Azure Administrator training?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-4" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>To avail scholarships for our Microsoft courses, please get in touch with us at <a href="mailto: support@oneitech.com" target="_blank"> support@oneitech.com</a>. The team shall send the forms and instructions across to you. Based upon the responses and answers that we receive, our panel of experts take a decision on the Grant. The entire process could take about 7 to 15 days.&nbsp;</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-5">5. Are group discounts available?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-5" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, group discounts are available and apply to groups as small as three (3) participants. The more participants that attend a training course, the greater the discount. By registering in groups, you can typically save up 20% to 30% on the course fees. For more details, please check out <a href="#" target="_blank">upcoming schedules</a>.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-6">6. Can I pay the course fees in instalments?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-6" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, instalment options are available for payment of course fee. To avail the instalment option, please get in touch with us at support@oneitech.com. The team will explain how the instalments work and provide timelines for your case.</p>
                                            <p>Typically, the number of instalments vary from 2 to 3, but the full amount must be paid before you complete the course.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
